description: A huge amount of skateboarders all over the globe consider Gino Iannucci the epitome of style and his 20+ years career speaks for itself. His Trilogy video part from 1996 is excellence and in the fourth installment of SkateMuzik, he sits down with G.Quagliano for the realest talk ever.
